#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kapptemplate; is an application to start development quickly using existing "
"templates providing basic repeatedly written code and a proper structure."
msgstr ""
"&kapptemplate; je aplikacija za hiter začetek razvoja z uporabo obstoječih "
"predlog, ki zagotavljajo osnovno večkrat napisano kodo in ustrezno strukturo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kapptemplate; picks up templates which are installed on your machine. Those "
"are often part of the development files for libraries or can be downloaded "
"&eg; from the website <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org\">store.kde.org</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&kapptemplate; pobere predloge, ki so nameščene na vašem računalniku. Te so "
"pogosto del razvojnih datotek za knjižnice ali pa jih je mogoče prenesti "
"&eg; s spletnega mesta <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org\">store.kde.org</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "Answer the wizard questions on each page and generate your template."
msgstr ""
"Odgovorite na vprašanja čarovnika na vsaki strani in ustvarite svojo "
"predlogo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <filename>README</filename> file in each template will allow you to find "
"out how to build the template. It will also give you links for tutorials "
"related to the project. After the project is generated, &kapptemplate;'s job "
"is finished and you are on your own to build it."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka <filename>README</filename> v vsaki predlogi vam bo omogočila, da "
"ugotovite, kako sestaviti predlogo. Prav tako vam bo ponudil povezave do "
"vadnic, povezanih s projektom. Ko je projekt ustvarjen, je delo "
"&kapptemplate; končano in sami ga lahko zgradite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kapptemplate;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kapptemplate;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kapptemplate; is a wizard. The first page of the wizard explains you that "
"&kapptemplate; will generate a base project. Click <guibutton>Next</"
"guibutton> to start generating your project. <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> "
"will stop the program and quit it. <guibutton>Help</guibutton> will display "
"this help handbook in &khelpcenter;."
msgstr ""
"&kapptemplate; je čarovnik. Na prvi strani čarovnika je razloženo, da "
"&kapptemplate; bo ustvaril osnovni projekt. Kliknite <guibutton>Naprej</"
"guibutton>, da začnete generirati svoj projekt. <guibutton>Prekliči</"
"guibutton> zaustavi program in ga zapre. <guibutton>Pomoč</guibutton> bo "
"prikazal ta priročnik za pomoč v &khelpcenter;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kapptemplate; first page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kapptemplate; prva stran</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kapptemplate; first page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kapptemplate; prva stran</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second page lists the available templates. On the right you can see the "
"template preview and below the template description. After you chose your "
"template, you are invited to enter the project name in the field at the "
"bottom."
msgstr ""
"Na drugi strani so navedene razpoložljive predloge. Na desni strani si lahko "
"ogledate predogled predloge in spodaj opis predloge. Ko izberete predlogo, "
"vas povabimo, da v polje na dnu vnesete ime projekta."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kapptemplate; second page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kapptemplate; druga stran</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kapptemplate; second page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kapptemplate; druga stran</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the third page, you are asked for the project version, the source folder "
"and the author name and email. If you filled &systemsettings; tab about your "
"personal information, it will be taken from there as default."
msgstr ""
"Na tretji strani boste morali vnesti različico projekta, izvorno mapo ter "
"ime in e-pošto avtorja. Če ste izpolnili &systemsettings; o vaših osebnih "
"podatkih, bodo od tam prevzeti kot privzeti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kapptemplate; third page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kapptemplate; tretja stran</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kapptemplate; third page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kapptemplate; tretja stran</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The fourth and last page gives you some feedback about the project "
"generation."
msgstr ""
"Četrta in zadnja stran vam daje nekaj povratnih informacij o ustvarjanju "
"projekta."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kapptemplate; fourth page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kapptemplate; četrta stran</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kapptemplate; fourth page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kapptemplate; četrta stran</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Then click <guibutton>Finish</guibutton> to close &kapptemplate;."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite <guibutton>Dokončaj</guibutton>, da zaprete &kapptemplate;."

